               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18261207-147-person874">
                  ROBERT 
                  BURGESS
               <interp inst="t18261207-147-person874" type="surname" value="BURGESS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18261207-147-person874" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18261207-147-person874" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the 8th of November, the prosecutor was coming down Butcher-row - I heard him cry Stop thief! I ran, and took the prisoner - I found in his pocket these scissars and spectacles, which he said his uncle gave him.</p>
